The paper focuses on optimizing analytics jobs in large-scale distributed systems, which involves data processing and storage. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
